Name: Dog Fight
About the game: Dog Fight The ultimate couch party game. Battle head to head with up to 8 players (cooperatively or versus). Or test your skill against waves of ever amassing enemies. Features - Up to 8 players local coop and via internet, LAN or locally - Computer controlled opponents - Multiple pickups to improve you combat effectiveness - Multiple game modes including: invasion, tag team, team free for all, rabbit
